DISCLAIMER — FAN PROJECT

This project is an unofficial, non-commercial fan-made trading-card game
inspired by Valve's Deadlock. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or
sponsored by Valve Corporation.

"Deadlock," all hero names, item names, and the bitmap art assets
distributed in `public/heroes/`, `public/spells/`, and `public/items/` are
the property of Valve Corporation. The art is sourced via the community-run
deadlock-api.com asset bucket and remains under Valve's copyright; it is
included here for illustrative, non-commercial fan use only.

The MIT license above applies ONLY to the source code in this repository —
the game engine, UI components, scripts, and tests authored by the project
maintainers. It does NOT grant any rights to the third-party art assets.

If you are a representative of Valve and would like the art removed,
please open an issue on this repository and I will comply promptly.
